0.5.1.name: wordpress/portfolio-press
0.5.1.description: Portfolio Press is a responsive theme for showcasing your photography, art, web sites, or other projects.  It also works nicely as a regular blog site.  An options panel is included for uploading logos and and changing the layout.  There's also support for the image, gallery and quote post formats.  Visit the demo site or watch the video screencast for set up instructions.
